### Compose PayloadCMS Admin Base List Filters for Collections

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/PLUGIN-DEVELOPMENT.md

This TypeScript snippet shows how to combine plugin-specific filters with an existing `baseListFilter` in PayloadCMS. It demonstrates how to add a tenant-specific filter to the `admin.baseListFilter` property, ensuring that all collection list views are automatically filtered by the current user's tenant. This pattern supports chaining multiple filter conditions.

```ts
// From plugin-multi-tenant
const existingBaseFilter = collection.admin?.baseListFilter
const tenantFilter = { tenant: { equals: req.user?.tenant } }

collection.admin = {
  ...collection.admin,
  baseListFilter: existingBaseFilter ? { and: [existingBaseFilter, tenantFilter] } : tenantFilter,
}
```

